Settings for Darwin (Mac OS X), using the GNU gfortran/f95 compiler
(part of the gcc 4.0 release) and GNU C++ compiler (g++).

Requires the following environment settings:

ESMF_COMPILER gfortran

Note:  We have *not* successfully compiled ESMF with this compiler
on the Mac platform.  If you do get this to work, please email
esmf_support@ucar.edu with your successful configuration and
any changes the files in this directory.

